__mod_name__ = "Music Player"
__help__ = """
          <b>„Äã**TwoSider V2.0** „Ää</b>
            
 TwoSider V2.0 can play music in your group's voice chat.
 
 Assistant name >> @SidPlay
 
<b> Setting up </b>

1) Promotr bot to admin.
2) Start a voice chat.
3) Try `/play [song name]` for the first time by an admin.
*) If @SidPlay joined your chat, then enjoy music, If not add @SidPlay to your group and retry!

<b> Commands </b>

=>> Song Playing üéß 

  /play: Play song using youtube music.
  /play [yt url] : Play the given yt url.
  /dplay: Play song via deezer.
  /splay: Play song via jio saavn.
  
=>> Playback ‚èØ

  /player: Open Settings menu of player.
  /skip: Skips the current track.
  /pause: Pause track.
  /resume: Resumes the paused track.
  /end: Stops media playback.
  /current: Shows the current Playing track.
  /playlist: Shows playlist.

=>> More tools üßë‚Äçüîß

  /admincache: Updates admin info of your group. Try if the bot doesn't recognize admin.
  /userbotjoin: Invite @SidPlay to your chat.

*Player cmd and all other cmds except /play, /current  and /playlist  are only for admins with manage group.

<b> PLEASE NOTE THIS SERVICE IS UNSTABLE AND CAN BE STOPPED ANYTIME </b>
"""
